The wives of prisoners, the mothers in the market committees, the seamstresses who keep the strike funds because the men keep losing them: Benita walks the vecindades and comes back with lists. The compañeros applaud the results and interrupt the women in the very next meeting, and Benita takes names of that, too.

@benita_memoria
title: Cincuenta y ocho veces
subtitle: Put her on a stage. She is the living proof that the Party predates its accusers.
choose-if: advisor_action_timer == 0
